.SH NAME
create_sg_component \- create SG componets for N5 device.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" create_sg_component
.BI "(struct nitrox_softreq *sr "  ","
.BI "struct nitrox_sgtable *sgtbl "  ","
.BI "int map_nents "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sr" 12
Request structure
.IP "sgtbl" 12
SG table
.IP "map_nents" 12
number of dma mapped entries
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Component structure

63     48 47     32 31    16 15      0
--------------------------------------
|   LEN0  |  LEN1  |  LEN2  |  LEN3  |
|-------------------------------------
|               PTR0                 |
--------------------------------------
|               PTR1                 |
--------------------------------------
|               PTR2                 |
--------------------------------------
|               PTR3                 |
--------------------------------------

Returns 0 if success or a negative errno code on error.
